        "mode": "All",
        "description": "Attempt to force the confit/ftpsState to the ftpsOnly value when a new website is created",
        "metadata": {
          "category": "github",
          "createdBy": "3d826307-2481-45a0-a271-bcf9333f914a",
          "createdOn": "2019-05-29T00:29:02.8182122Z",
          "updatedBy": null,
